-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3-156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-1-3.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eNext, press the mixture into balls. I rolled mine by hand and ended up with 28 balls from these ingredients. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/traditional-rum-balls/?tp_image_id=136462\" data-pin-title=\"Traditional Rum Balls\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.-.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.--156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls.-.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLast, roll your finished balls in cocoa powder (you may also use powdered sugar) as a garnish. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eStore at room temperature until ready to serve. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-for-making\"\u003eTips for Making \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou can store these balls in a container at room temperature for up to one week. If you prefer to make them ahead (or save some of your batch), you can also freeze them for up to three months.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eSome people like to keep their balls in individual mini cupcake liners (so they look like a box of chocolates) for serving. This a a great option if making them for a party.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eWhat is a substitute for Nilla wafers? If you don’t have Nilla wafer cookies on hand, you can use a similar crispy store-bought cookie. You may also try it with a soft cookie, but the closest substitution would be another crispy cookie.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/traditional-rum-balls/?tp_image_id=136463\" data-pin-title=\"Traditional Rum Balls\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rum-Balls-how-to-make.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\